<h4><br>Homemade Bone Meal Powder</h4>



<p>Bone meal is crushed animal bones that have been sterilized by heat treatment to kill any harmful pathogen. This powder when applied to plants acts as a slow-release fertilizer. Bone meal is rich in phosphorous and calcium both of which play a significant role in plant growth lifecycle. You can make bone meal fertilizer in your home quite easily. </p>



